::DrillBit::

He looked at KitKat. He was lucky. He had a fiance who was brave, smart,
and beutiful. He was about to answer her when Dark Mouse walked in and
gave a report.
"New bots, huh? If we get a response then I will go we'll go meet with
them."
He then thought of something. His best friend(Star Scream) had not been
seen since DrillBit had left the battle.
He then saw that he and others were returning. He was glad. He had
something to discuss with StarScream.
